high_descs: Turn around and go to the coffeetable.
Pick up the ladle on the coffee table.
Turn around and go into the room on your right which is the bathroom and go to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink rinse it off and then take it out of the sink.
Leave the room take a right and go into the sidetable on the right straight ahead.
Put the ladle on the back of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a ladle and put it on the back of the side table.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the coffee table
Pick the ladle from the coffee table
Turn around and go straight and turn left to reach the sink
Put the ladle into the sink and rinse it off
Take back the ladle turn left then turn right again turn right to go to the bedroom
Keep the ladle on the side table beside the bed
anns.task_desc: Pick the ladle rinse it off and keep it on the side table

high_descs: Turn right to reach the dining table.
Pick up the ladle from the dining table.
Turn left to reach the bathroom and face the sink on the left.
Wash the ladle in the sink and take it out.
Turn left and head down the passage on the right and turn right to walk into the bedroom to reach the side table.
Put the ladle on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed ladle on the side table.
